SQL_STMT_U.val: select distinct DocType,DocEntry from [@TMP_HIERARKI_DOC] where USERID=':1' group by DocType,DocEntry

select H.DocType,H.DocEntry,H.BaseType,H.BaseEntry, S.DESCRIPTION, T.DocNum, T.DocDate, T.DocStatus, T.Canceled, T.DocTotal, T.NumAtCard from ( select distinct DocType,DocEntry,BaseType,BaseEntry from [@TMP_HIERARKI_DOC] where USERID=':1' ) H left join sys_gcm (nolock) S on H.DocType = S.GCM_ID and S.CONDITION = 'OBJTYPE' inner join ALLDOC_VIEW T (nolock) on H.DocType = T.ObjType and H.DocEntry = T.DocEntry

Text.valUnicode: var Win10 = ( navigator.userAgent.match(/(Windows Phone 10|Windows NT 10)/g) ? true : false );
